{"data":{"items":[{"content":"{\"images\":[],\"audios\":[],\"imageTotalCount\":0,\"audioTotalCount\":0,\"text\":\"像你这样悟性高的太少啦  只能通过有为法入手，最后都是走向无为法才能得到笔法的真谛。\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2023-10-22T11:38:14+0800","evaluateStatus":1,"id":13322868,"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20220602/2022060208442182070043.jpg","ccUserName":"jnukant001","identity":1,"nickName":"一定写好字吖","userId":151885219},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"images\":[],\"audios\":[],\"imageTotalCount\":0,\"audioTotalCount\":0,\"text\":\"最后都是无招胜有招🇨🇳\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2023-10-22T11:36:06+0800","evaluateStatus":1,"id":13322861,"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20220602/2022060208442182070043.jpg","ccUserName":"jnukant001","identity":1,"nickName":"一定写好字吖","userId":151885219},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"太厉害了！！！\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2023-10-22T19:25:09+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":13323963,"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20231024/2023102401502466126073.jpg","ccUserName":"而归儿","identity":2,"nickName":"而归【0087】","userId":158130835},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"哇哦能帮到你我很开心😆 \",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2023-10-22T14:11:02+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":13323235,"parentUserInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20231207/2023120706310930817114.jpg","ccUserName":"JayenLoo","identity":0,"nickName":"知临1140","userId":11026376},"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20230919/202309190704292813202.jpg","ccUserName":"手机用户4468gugdf","identity":0,"nickName":"兔斯基爱写字0830","userId":166518750},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"熟能生巧之后就自然过渡至自然状态了。跟练功一样，刚开始很多注意事项在熟练之后就不需要太过于注意动作是否标准，而是抓住一个核心感受就够了。 少部分学生可能不需要讲太多，只需要一句话，就能体悟那种感觉然后坚持练习就到了，而大部分学生，缺乏这种先天的禀赋，所以方法次第就很重要。 \",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2023-10-22T13:42:12+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":13323148,"parentUserInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20230919/202309190704292813202.jpg","ccUserName":"手机用户4468gugdf","identity":0,"nickName":"兔斯基爱写字0830","userId":166518750},"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20220602/2022060208442182070043.jpg","ccUserName":"jnukant001","identity":1,"nickName":"一定写好字吖","userId":151885219},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"不知道为啥我经常在练习时想到道家的治国理念“无为而治”，脑子里这个想法和老师说的是一致的，有些练习是需要“刻意为之”的，但我们追求的结果应该是心手达情自然而然产生的\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2023-10-22T13:26:34+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":13323128,"parentUserInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20220602/2022060208442182070043.jpg","ccUserName":"jnukant001","identity":1,"nickName":"一定写好字吖","userId":151885219},"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20230919/202309190704292813202.jpg","ccUserName":"手机用户4468gugdf","identity":0,"nickName":"兔斯基爱写字0830","userId":166518750},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"刚刚参考了你说的，再看了昨晚的录屏，又把第一节课看了一遍，抓到窍门，嘿嘿。谢谢你！\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2023-10-22T13:18:56+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":13323121,"parentUserInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20230919/202309190704292813202.jpg","ccUserName":"手机用户4468gugdf","identity":0,"nickName":"兔斯基爱写字0830","userId":166518750},"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20231207/2023120706310930817114.jpg","ccUserName":"JayenLoo","identity":0,"nickName":"知临1140","userId":11026376},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"群里应该有录屏的吧，你把老师说的那些话多看几遍，然后你着重感受下你行笔中呼吸的节奏是怎么样的，是提笔时先吸气按下去呼气还是反着来的，我的个人感受是这样的，如果呼吸节奏快了行笔速度就快，因为不停的换气会使身体微微颤动心跳也会快手就抖，所以放慢速度最重要的是调节呼吸节奏。或者这么说，调节呼吸节奏就是调节身体里的一股气，气息稳了心态自然稳，心态稳了手就不抖了，整个身体的状态都是放松的，速度自然就慢了\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2023-10-22T13:16:57+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":13323088,"parentUserInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20231207/2023120706310930817114.jpg","ccUserName":"JayenLoo","identity":0,"nickName":"知临1140","userId":11026376},"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20230919/202309190704292813202.jpg","ccUserName":"手机用户4468gugdf","identity":0,"nickName":"兔斯基爱写字0830","userId":166518750},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"那正确的做法应该是什么呢？昨晚老师说的我有一点点get不到\\n\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2023-10-22T10:48:13+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":13322565,"parentUserInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20230919/202309190704292813202.jpg","ccUserName":"手机用户4468gugdf","identity":0,"nickName":"兔斯基爱写字0830","userId":166518750},"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20231207/2023120706310930817114.jpg","ccUserName":"JayenLoo","identity":0,"nickName":"知临1140","userId":11026376},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"早～\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2023-10-22T10:00:48+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":13322472,"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20231011/2023101104351043195715.jpg","ccUserName":"穿堂风eyhzn","identity":0,"nickName":"阿猫阿狗【1112】","userId":91042945},"userPower":0},{"content":"{\"text\":\"想知道这个呼吸到底是怎么回事🥲\",\"hasMore\":false}","createdTime":"2023-10-22T09:48:15+0800","evaluateStatus":0,"id":13322399,"userInfo":{"avatar":"https://cc.hjfile.cn/cc/img/20231207/2023120706310930817114.jpg","ccUserName":"JayenLoo","identity":0,"nickName":"知临1140","userId":11026376},"userPower":0}],"nextPage":false},"message":"success","status":0}